   "text": "UniFi sends CEF to SC4S on 1514; SC4S forwards over HEC on 8088 into bounded network indexes. Routing puts new Network, OS, and Protect events in netops instead of main, and Enterprise Security loaded once the VM had 6 vCPU.",
